Description: For sell is a MJT Customs Telecaster with a double bound alder body, maple neck (C shape) with a rosewood fret board, bone nut and all aged hardware from MJT Customs. This is a beautiful custom guitar with medium wear and awesome checking throughout the finish to give it a great aged look! This is a USA SALE ONLY!! I WILL NOT SHIP OUTSIDE THE UNITED STATES of AMERICA! Shipping will be $50 flat. The case is not the best but it works.. it has deployed with me 2 times to Afghanistan with no issues. The guitar will ship with a case and a Vintage style Dunlap BMF leather strap. If you have any questions please ask. Only selling this guitar because I’m getting into acoustic guitars. Capacitor and pickup details below. The controls were handmade by Steve from Tundratone with 4 way telecaster switch and a ITW .047 paper capacitor. NOS 1960's. 047 uF Genuine ITW Paper capacitors. Illinois Tool Works (ITW) Paper dielectric capacitors.
